keyFacts: The document is a TECS (Treasury Enforcement Communications System) person query record generated by U.S. Customs and Border Protection on September 23, 2019.
Ghislaine Maxwell is listed as a 'NON-SUSPECT, PRIVATE AIRCRAFT INSPECTION' subject with category 'NP'.
The record indicates Maxwell was 'NOT ON PRIMARY' action list at the time of the query.
The record contains an earlier date of July 22, 2002, suggesting previous entries or updates in the system.
The document shows Maxwell's age as 57 years old at the time of the 2019 query.
